body_html:
Use Python 3.5.X 64bit on Windows.

For me, this version is working with Tensorflow, I had this same issue, but installing an older python solved it:

Python 3.5.4 (Aug  8 2017) 64 bit
Tensorflow 1.11.0

So python must be 64 bit and 3.5.X at the same time.

body:
Use Python 3.5.X 64bit on Windows.

For me, this version is working with Tensorflow, I had this same issue, but installing an older python solved it:
```
Python 3.5.4 (Aug  8 2017) 64 bit
Tensorflow 1.11.0
```
So python must be 64 bit and 3.5.X at the same time.
